{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund local environmental education initiatives and clean-up campaigns",
        "additional_details": "I think there is a lack of respect to the environment from many young people, and that some educational programmes might help to reduce this. Our roadsides bear witness to this issue.\r\n \r\nWe want to see environmental education programs targeting young people to instil respect for nature and provide the proper waste disposal habits from an early age.\r\n \r\nWe also want to see investment in clean-up campaigns, including to cleaning up roads with high volumes of litter, to protect wildlife from harmful waste.\r\n",
        "background": "I want the Government to provide funding to local authorities for local environmental education initiatives and clean-up campaigns.",
